t to the agent\\n21: 6. Displays the response\\n22: \\n23: Implement the `status` command that:\\n24: 1. Loads workspace metadata\\n25: 2. Checks if agent is published\\n26: 3. Queries the target provider for deployment status\\n27: 4. Displays status in a Rich Table\\n28: \\n29: ### Value\\n30: \\n31: - **Direct Agent Interaction**: POST JSON payloads to invoke agents\\n32: - **Flexible Headers**: Support custom HTTP headers for authentication\\n33: - **Status Monitoring**: Real-time deployment status check\\n34: - **Dual Provider Support**: Works with b...\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/results/runs/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z_logs/AR-027_ST-4.log:\n  Line 4: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775864345021,\"sessionID\":\"ses_2863f59e7ffebxAKmtvX29SnpI\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d79c0adb4001gNKGpIN7MG33ov\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d79c0a704001NBICTj1lpe8PTV\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_2863f59e7ffebxAKmtvX29SnpI\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"task\",\"callID\":\"call_1eae1e927bd842aa886614da\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"description\":\"Explore agentcube project structure\",\"prompt\":\"Explore the agentcube project structure to understand:\\n1. The overall project layout and directory structure\\n2. The sdk-python module structure and existing patterns\\n3. Any existing CodeInterpreterClient or similar client implementations\\n4. Test patterns used in the project\\n5. Any existing tasks.md or similar planning documents to match format\\n\\nSearch thoroughly in the workspace root /home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z and look for:\\n- sdk-python directory\\n- Any client implementations\\n- Test files\\n- tasks.md or similar files\\n\\nReturn a comprehensive summary of the project structure, existing patterns, and any relevant code examples.\",\"subagent_type\":\"explore\"},\"output\":\"task_id: ses_2863f4305ffePLBUZ5Js9Ex4Is (for resuming to continue this task if needed)\\n\\n<ta