0: - **Module**: `cmd/cli`\\n11: - **Language**: Python\\n12: - **Size**: M\\n13: \\n14: ---\\n15: \\n16: ## Background\\n17: \\n18: The `invoke` command sends JSON payloads to deployed agents via the AgentCube Router or standard Kubernetes Service. The `status` command retrieves and displays the current status of deployed agents. Both commands work with either the AgentCube provider (AgentRuntime CR) or the standard Kubernetes provider (Deployment + Service).\\n19: \\n20: ---\\n21: \\n22: ## Requirements\\n23: \\n24: ### AR-023-001: invoke CLI interface\\n25: \\n26: The system SHALL expose the `invoke` command via Typer with specific options.\\n27: \\n28: #### Scenario: AR-023-001-A — Invoke command options\\n29: \\n30: - **GIVEN** the user runs `kubectl-agentcube invoke --help`\\n31: - **THEN** the CLI SHALL display:\\n32:   - `-f, --workspace PATH` — Path to agent workspace (default: \\\".\\\")\\n33:   - `--payload JSON` — JSON-formatted input passed to the agent (default: \\\"{}\\\")\\n34:   - `--header KEY:VALUE` — Custom HTTP headers (repeatable)\\n35:   - `--provider ...\n  Line 39: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775863938710,\"sessionID\":\"ses_286447524ffeh9UaDmgYVkh66a\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d79bc91eb001GU2jKkBPPjA22p\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d79bc7d00001jAIEyiWMo5zULn\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_286447524ffeh9UaDmgYVkh66a\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"write\",\"callID\":\"toolu_0091e5f54754443abffb3d63\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"content\":\"# AR-023 — CLI Invoke/Status Command\\n\\n- **AR ID**: AR-023\\n- **Module**: cmd/cli\\n- **Language**: Python\\n- **Size**: M\\n- **Status**: ST-1 Completed (design.md)\\n\\n## 1. Architecture\\n\\n### 1.1 Overview\\n\\nThe `invoke` command sends JSON payloads to deployed agents via the AgentCube Router or standard Kubernetes Service. The `status` command retrieves and displays the current status of deployed agents. Both commands work with either the AgentCube provider (AgentRuntime CR) or the standard Kubernetes provider (Deployment + Service).\\n\\n### 1.2 Package Structure\\n\\n```\\ncmd/cli/\\n├── pyproject.toml                              # Project metadata, dependencies\\n├── agentcube/\\n│   ├── __init__.py                             # Package version __version__, exports\\n│   ├── cli/\\n│   │   ├── __init__.py                         # CLI subpackage marker\\n│   │   └── main.py                             # Typer app, invoke/status commands\\n│   ├── runtime/\\n│   │   ├── invoke_runtime.py                  # InvokeRuntime\\n│   │   └── status_runtime.py                  # StatusRuntime\\n│   └── services/\\n│       ├── metadata_service.py                # AgentMetadata, MetadataService\\n│       ├── k8s_provider.py                    # KubernetesProvider\\n│       └── agentcube_provider.py               # AgentCubeProvider\\n```\\n\\n### 1.3 Provider Types\\n\\n| Provider | Invocation Target | Status Target |\\n|----------|-------------------|---------------|\\n| `agentcube` | AgentRuntime CR via Router | AgentRuntime CR |\\n| `k8s` | Kubernetes Service | Kubernetes Deployment |\\n\\n## 2. Command Specifications\\n\\n### 2.1 invoke Command\\n\\nThe `invok...\n  Line 42: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775863942697,\"sessionID\":\"ses_286447524ffeh9UaDmgYVkh66a\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d79bd49e1001igF8mWg5pLjmNh\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d79bd3ec9001esx1sO30l70oUv\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_286447524ffeh9UaDmgYVkh66a\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"toolu_d8fc5854e7ef4a749698ff3a\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-023/design.md\",\"limit\":50},\"output\":\"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-023/design.md</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: # AR-023 — CLI Invoke/Status Command\\n2: \\n3: - **AR ID**: AR-0