3: | `agentcube/runtime/__init__.py` | Re-exports runtimes + `MetadataOptions` |\\n24: | `agentcube/runtime/pack_runtime.py` | `PackRuntime` |\\n25: | `agentcube/runtime/build_runtime.py` | `BuildRuntime` |\\n26: | `agentcube/runtime/publish_runtime.py` | `PublishRuntime` |\\n27: | `agentcube/runtime/invoke_runtime.py` | `InvokeRuntime` |\\n28: | `agentcube/runtime/status_runtime.py` | `StatusRuntime` |\\n29: | `agentcube/services/__init__.py` | Services package docstring |\\n30: | `agentcube/services/metadata_service.py` | `AgentMetadata`, `MetadataServi...\n  Line 23: {\"type\":\"text\",\"timestamp\":1775863675339,\"sessionID\":\"ses_286474d8fffeKqLRB2b8M5keEa\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d79b9383b001v5Ejb9thNBU5Uz\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d79b92f97001sY9bigv574NXuo\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_286474d8fffeKqLRB2b8M5keEa\",\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Now I have a good understanding of the codebase. Let me write the proposal.md for AR-023:\",\"time\":{\"start\":1775863675338,\"end\":1775863675338}}}\n  Line 24: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775863723659,\"sessionID\":\"ses_286474d8fffeKqLRB2b8M5keEa\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d79b939cc001y5MmyFI0RxCztk\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d79b92f97001sY9bigv574NXuo\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_286474d8fffeKqLRB2b8M5keEa\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"write\",\"callID\":\"toolu_ce4f4e5367de4477b7ebcd2b\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"content\":\"# Proposal: AR-023 — CLI Invoke/Status Command\\n\\n## Summary\\n\\nImplement the `invoke` and `status` commands for the AgentCube CLI (`kubectl-agentcube`) that enable users to interact with and monitor published AI agents.\\n\\n## Purpose\\n\\n### Background\\n\\nThe AgentCube CLI (`kubectl-agentcube`) provides commands for the complete agent lifecycle: pack → build → publish → **invoke** → **status**. The `invoke` and `status` commands are the final two steps, enabling agent interaction and status monitoring.\\n\\n### Goal\\n\\nImplement the `invoke` command that:\\n1. Loads workspace metadata from `agent_metadata.yaml`\\n2. Parses and validates JSON payload\\n3. Parses custom HTTP headers\\n4. Resolves the agent endpoint from metadata\\n5. Sends HTTP POST request to the agent\\n6. Displays the response\\n\\nImplement the `status` command that:\\n1. Loads workspace metadata\\n2. Checks if agent is published\\n3. Queries the target provider for deployment status\\n4. Displays status in a Rich Table\\n\\n### Value\\n\\n- **Direct Agent Interaction**: POST JSON payloads to invoke agents\\n- **Flexible Headers**: Support custom HTTP headers for authentication\\n- **Status Monitoring**: Real-time deployment status check\\n- **Dual Provider Support**: Works with both AgentCube CRD and K8s deployments\\n- **Consistency**: Follows existing CLI patterns and design specs\\n\\n---\\n\\n## Scope\\n\\n### In-Scope\\n\\n| Component | Path | Description |\\n|-----------|------|-------------|\\n| Invoke command | `agentcube/cli/main.py` | Typer command binding |\\n| Invoke runtime | `agentcube/runtime/invoke_runtime.py` | Core invoke logic |\\n| Status command | `agentcube/cli/main.p...\n  Line 27: {\"type\":\"text\",\"timestamp\":1775863729185,\"sessionID\":\"ses_286474d8fffeKqLRB2b8M5keEa\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d79b9ffc6001zuc9sHQiigbGAO\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d79b9f6bb001aE2sXS0rIZpNfp\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_286474d8fffeKqLRB2b8M5keEa\",\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"I've written the proposal.md for AR-023 (CLI invoke/status commands). The proposal includes:\\n\\n1. **Summary**: Overview of the invoke and status commands for the AgentCube CLI\\n2. **Scope**: Components, CLI interfaces, and APIs for both commands\\n3. **Impact Analysis**: Dependencies, upstream/downstream, and risks\\n4. **Implementation Plan**: Phases for InvokeRuntime, StatusRuntime, and CLI integration\\n5. **Acceptance Criteria**: 16 test scenarios for invoke (AI-001 to AI-009) and status (AS-001 to AS-007)\\n6. **Technical Design**: Flow diagrams and code samples for endpoint resolution and header parsing\\n7. **Timeline Estimate**: 6-10 hours total\\n8. **Existing Implementation Status**: Notes on current code and identified gaps\\n\\nKey gaps identified:\\n- Fix UnboundLocalError bug in `invoke_runtime.py:62`\\n- Add invoke/status commands to `main.py` with Typer bindings\\n- Implement Rich Table output for status\\n- Proper exit codes for error conditions\",\"time\":{\"start\":1775863729183,\"end\":1775863729183}}}\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/results/runs/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z_logs/AR-023_ST-0.log:\n  Line 19: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775863633518,\"sessionID\":\"ses_28647b8dbffe1S5igWhULpE0D8\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d79b8937d0016EJQZKD4Bp2dQ5\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d79b88490001XuIA4M1O4e41aa\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_28647b8dbffe1S5igWhULpE0D8\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"bash\",\"callID\":\"toolu_4934b807a64140b2879c98e1\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"command\":\"mkdir -p changes/AR-023\",\"description\":\"Create AR-023 change directory\"},\"output\":\"\",\"metadata\":{\"output\":\"\",\"exit\":0,\"description\":\"Create AR-023 change directory\",\"truncated\":false},\"title\":\"Create AR-023 change directory\",\"time\":{\"start\":1775863633506,\"end\":1775863633516}}}}\n  Line 22: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775863635917,\"sessionID\":\"ses_28647b8dbffe1S5igWhULpE0D8\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d79b89ddb001pNmGPgmfUDZdfv\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d79b896a4001LKBAwiPAhmsrlS\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_28647b8dbffe1S5igWhULpE0D8\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"bash\",\"callID\":\"toolu_c6dc3c62287a490fa9df5470\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"command\":\"ls -la changes/AR-023/\",\"description\":\"Verify AR-023 directory created\"},\"output\":\"total 8\\ndrwxr-xr-x  2 root root 4096 Apr 11 07:27 .\\ndrwxr-xr-x 25 root root 4096 Apr 11 07:27 ..\\n\",\"metadata\":{\"output\":\"total 8\\ndrwxr-xr-x  2 root root 4096 Apr 11 07:27 .\\ndrwxr-xr-x 25 root root 4096 Ap