a-spec.md</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: # AR-023: CLI invoke/status 命令 — Delta Spec\\n2: \\n3: ## Context\\n4: \\n5: - **Module:** `cmd/cli`\\n6: - **Language:** Python\\n7: - **Size:** M\\n8: - **Base specs:** `cli-toolkit/spec.md`, `cli-toolkit/design.md`\\n9: \\n10: ## Scope\\n11: \\n12: This delta spec covers the `invoke` and `status` CLI commands, their runtime classes (`InvokeRuntime`, `StatusRuntime`), and associated provider integrations (`AgentCubeProvider`, `KubernetesProvider`).\\n13: \\n14: ---\\n15: \\n16: ## invoke Command\\n17: \\n18: ### Requirement: invoke command entry point\\n19: \\n20: The system SHALL provide an `invoke` subcommand that POSTs JSON payload to the published agent endpoint, supporting both `agentcube` (AgentRuntime CR) and `k8s` (Deployment/Service) providers.\\n21: \\n22: #### Scenario: invoke options and defaults\\n23: \\n24: - **GIVEN** the user runs `invoke`\\n25: - **THEN** defaults SHALL be:\\n26:   - `workspace` = `\\\".\\\"` (`-f` / `--workspace`, `str`)\\n27:   - `payload` = `\\\"{}\\\"` (`--payload`, `str`)\\n28:   - `header_list` = `None` (`--header`, repeatable `List[str]`)\\n29:   - `provider` = `\\\"agentcube\\\"` (`--provider`, `str`)\\n30:   - `verbose` = `False` (`--verbose`, `bool`)\\n31: \\n32: #### Scenario: payload JSON parsing\\n33: \\n34: - **GIVEN** the user provides `--payload '{\\\"input\\\": \\\"hello\\\"}'`\\n35: - **WHEN** the command parses it\\n36: - **THEN** the system SHALL deserialize it to...\n  Line 15: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775857701048,\"sessionID\":\"ses_286a2df52ffevi33M7N6XqWgXp\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d795e0c0b001gf9aT1FcF5Y0R5\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d795df9be0015HQf40WL7VjqgS\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_286a2df52ffevi33M7N6XqWgXp\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"call_46336a12a7ae4479ade58059\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-023/delta-spec.md\"},\"output\":\"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-023/delta-spec.md</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: # AR-023: CLI invoke/status 命令 — Delta Spec\\n2: \\n3: ## Context\\n4: \\n5: - **Module:** `cmd/cli`\\n6: - **Language:** Python\\n7: - **Size:** M\\n8: - **Base specs:** `cli-toolkit/design.md`, `cli-toolkit/spec.md`\\n9: \\n10: ## Delta Requirements\\n11: \\n12: ### Requirement: `invoke` command\\n13: \\n14: The system SHALL provide an `invoke` subcommand that sends an HTTP request to a deployed agent endpoint.\\n15: \\n16: #### Scenario: Command signature\\n17: - **GIVEN** the CLI is installed\\n18: - **WHEN** the user runs `agentcube invoke --help`\\n19: - **THEN** it SHALL show options for workspace, input/prompt, and verbose\\n20: \\n21: #### Scenario: Invoke with endpoint from metadata\\n22: - **GIVEN** the workspace has been published and `agent_metadata.yaml` contains `agent_endpoint`\\n23: - **WHEN** the user runs `agentcube invoke -f <workspace> --prompt \\\"hello\\\"`\\n24: - **THEN** the system SHALL send an HTTP POST request to the endpoint and display the response\\n25: \\n26: #### Scenario: Invoke without published endpoint\\n27: - **GIVEN** the workspace has not been published or `agent_endpoint` is missing\\n28: - **WHEN** the user runs `agentcube invoke`\\n29: - **THEN** the system SHALL raise a `ValueError` indicating the agent has not been published\\n30: \\n31: ### Requirement: `status` command\\n32: \\n33: The system SHALL provide a `status` subcom...\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/results/runs/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z_logs/AR-024_ST-1.log:\n  Line 10: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775857582846,\"sessionID\":\"ses_286a49312ffemU3qSvKZfL7QjS\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d795c3bec001vrZWPah521r817\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d795c24bc001h4x6T6pMVgjSb5\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_286a49312ffemU3qSvKZfL7QjS\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"call_cafdba5a477d420686c8756c\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/proposal.md\"},\"output\":\"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/proposal.md</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: # AR-023: CLI invoke/status 命令\\n2: \\n3: ## Purpose\\n4: \\n5: 为 AgentCube Python CLI（`kubectl-agentcube`）实现 `invoke` 和 `status` 两个子命令，补全 Agent 从打包、构建、发布到调用和状态查询的完整生命周期。\\n6: \\n7: 当前 CLI 已实现 `pack`、`build`、`publish` 命令，但用户部署 Agent 后无法通过 CLI 验证其是否正常工作或查看运行状态。本 AR 补齐最后两个关键操作。\\n8: \\n9: ## Scope\\n10: \\n11: ### In Scope\\n12: \\n13: 1. **`invoke` 命令**\\n14:    - 向已部署的 Agent 发送 HTTP POST 请求\\n15:    - 支持 `--payload` 传递 JSON 输入（默认 `\\\"{}\\\"`）\\n16:    - 支持 `--header` 添加自定义 HTTP Header（可重复指定）\\n17:    - 支持 `--provider` 选择 `agentcube`（AgentRuntime CR）或 `k8s`（标准 Deployment/Service）\\n18:    - AgentCube Provider 自动将 endpoint 重写为 `/v1/namespaces/{namespace}/agent-runtimes/{agent_name}/invocations/`\\n19:    - 若元数据包含 `session_id`，自动添加 `X-Agentcube-Session-Id` Header\\n20:    - 打印响应结果，异常通过 `_handle_error` 处理\\n21: \\n22: 2. **`status` 命令**\\n23:    - 加载 workspace 元数据（`agent_metadata.yaml`）\\n24:    - 根据 `--provider` 查询对应资源状态\\n25:    - AgentCube Provider：通过 `AgentCubeProvider.get_agent_runtime` 查询 CR 状态\\n26:    - K8s Provider：通过 `KubernetesProvider.get_agent_status` 查询 Deployment/Service 状态\\n27:    - 使用 Rich Table 渲染状态信息\\n28:    - `not_published` 或 `error` 状态时打印提示并 `typer.Exit(1)`\\n29: \\n30: 3. **错误处理**\\n31:    - `invoke`：JSON payload 解析失败、Header 格式错误直接退出码 1\\n32:    - 运行时异常统一走 `_handle_error(e, command_name, verbose)`\\n33: \\n34: ### Out of Scope\\n35: \\n36: - 修复 `InvokeRuntime._invoke_agent_via_agentcub...\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/results/runs/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z_logs/AR-014_ST-7.log:\n  Line 15: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\