.md\\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-021/delta-spec.md\\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-021/proposal.md\\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-021/design.md\\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-020/tasks.md\\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-020/del...\n  Line 8: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775857488321,\"sessionID\":\"ses_286a547f1ffeZpobFdTX1gJ7fx\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d795acdd3001vULNFn0btZEts2\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d795ac4cf001rXStxP6u3Htbfl\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_286a547f1ffeZpobFdTX1gJ7fx\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"call_ce1fcc15467347abb58a62f1\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-023/proposal.md\"},\"output\":\"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-023/proposal.md</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: # AR-023 — CLI invoke/status 命令\\n2: \\n3: **Module:** cmd/cli\\n4: **Language:** Python\\n5: **Size:** M\\n6: \\n7: ## 目的\\n8: \\n9: 为 AgentCube CLI (`kubectl-agentcube`) 实现 `invoke` 和 `status` 两个子命令。`invoke` 用于向已部署的 agent 发送请求并获取响应，`status` 用于查询 agent 的运行状态和部署信息。\\n10: \\n11: ## 范围\\n12: \\n13: ### 包含\\n14: \\n15: 1. `invoke` Typer 命令实现\\n16: 2. `status` Typer 命令实现\\n17: 3. `InvokeRuntime` 类实现\\n18: 4. `StatusRuntime` 类增强\\n19: \\n20: ### 不包含\\n21: \\n22: - `pack` / `build` / `publish` 命令的实现（由 AR-020 / AR-021 / AR-022 覆盖）\\n23: - Go 二进制入口\\n24: - CI/CD pipeline 变更\\n25: \\n26: ## 架构概要\\n27: \\n28: ```\\n29: CLI Layer (Typer)\\n30: ├── invoke() command → InvokeRuntime.invoke()\\n31: └── status() command → StatusRuntime.status()\\n32: \\n33: Runtime Layer\\n34: ├── InvokeRuntime — 发送 HTTP 请求到已部署的 agent endpoint\\n35: └── StatusRuntime — 查询 K8s CR 或 Deployment 状态\\n36: ```\\n37: \\n38: ## 上游依赖\\n39: \\n40: - **AR-022 (`publish` 命令)** — 依赖 publish 部署后的 agent endpoint 和 metadata\\n41: \\n42: ## 状态\\n43: \\n44: - [ ] 提案审查\\n45: - [ ] 实现\\n46: - [ ] 验证\\n\\n(End of file - total 46 lines)\\n</content>\",\"metadata\":{\"preview\":\"# AR-023 — CLI invoke/status 命令\\n\\n**Module:** cmd/cli\\n**Language:** Python\\n**Size:** M\\n\\n## 目的\\n\\n为 AgentCube CLI (`kubectl-agentcube`) 实现 `invoke` 和 `status` 两个子命令。`invoke` 用于向已部署的 agent 发送请求并获取响应，`status` 用于查询 agent 的运行状态和部署信息。\\n\\n## 范围\\n\\n### 包含\\n\\n1. `invoke` Type...\n  Line 9: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775857489641,\"sessionID\":\"ses_286a547f1ffeZpobFdTX1gJ7fx\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d795ad22b001kbAgjZSQDQiQ4c\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d795ac4cf001rXStxP6u3Htbfl\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_286a547f1ffeZpobFdTX1gJ7fx\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"call_965788d5290344d2853a38bf\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-023/design.md\"},\"output\":\"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-023/design.md</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: # AR-023 — CLI invoke/status 命令 — Design\\n2: \\n3: ## Overview\\n4: \\n5: The `invoke` command sends HTTP POST requests to a deployed agent endpoint and displays the response. The `status` command queries the deployment status of an agent from Kubernetes or workspace metadata and renders it as a Rich Table. Together they complete the agent lifecycle pipeline: `pack → build → publish → invoke/status`.\\n6: \\n7: Both commands are **not yet implemented** — this design specifies the full technical implementation.\\n8: \\n9: ---\\n10: \\n11: ## Architecture\\n12: \\n13: ### 2.1 Data Flow\\n14: \\n15: ```\\n16: ┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\\n17: │                          CLI (Typer)                                  │\\n18: │   kubectl-agentcube invoke -f <ws> --payload '{}' [--header ...]     │\\n19: │   kubectl-agentcube status -f <ws> [--provider agentcube|k8s]        │\\n20: └────────────────────────┬─────────────────────────────────────────────┘\\n21:                          │\\n22:           ┌──────────────┴──────────────┐\\n23:           ▼                             ▼\\n24: ┌─────────────────────┐       ┌─────────────────────┐\\n25: │    InvokeRuntime    │       │    StatusRuntime    │\\n26: │                     │       │                     │\\n27: │ .invoke()           │       │ .get_status()       │\\n28: │  ├─ _valid...\n  Line 10: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775857491008,\"sessionID\":\"ses_286a547f1ffeZpobFdTX1gJ7fx\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d795ad76a001ugaC5uj4C6jbTd\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d795ac4cf001rXStxP6u3Htbfl\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_286a547f1ffeZpobFdTX1gJ7fx\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"call_68a6c32af32a4b6b9a04d96f\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-023/delta-spec.md\"},\"output\":\"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-023/delta-spec.md</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: # AR-023: CLI invoke/status 命令 — Delta Spec\\n2: \\n3: ## Context\\n4: \\n5: - **Module:** `cmd/cli`\\n6: - **Language:** Python\\n7: - **Size:** M\\n8: - **Base specs:** `cli-toolkit/design.md`, `cli-toolkit/spec.md`\\n9: \\n10: ## Delta Requirements\\n11: \\n12: ### Requirement: `invoke` command\\n13: \\n14: The system SHALL provide an `invoke` subcommand that sends an HTTP request to a deployed agent endpoint.\\n15: \\n16: #### Scenario: Command signature\\n17: - **GIVEN** the CLI is installed\\n18: - **WHEN** the user runs `agentcube invoke --help`\\n19: - **THEN** it SHALL show options for workspace, input/prompt, and verbose\\n20: \\n21: #### Scenario: Invoke with endpoint from metadata\\n22: - **GIVEN** the workspace has been published and `agent_metadata.yaml` contains `agent_endpoint`\\n23: - **WHEN** the user runs `agentcube invoke -f <workspace> --prompt \\\"hello\\\"`\\n24: - **THEN** the system SHALL send an HTTP POST request to the endpoint and display the response\\n25: \\n26: #### Scenario: Invoke without published endpoint\\n27: - **GIVEN** the workspace has not been published or `agent_endpoint` is missing\\n28: - **WHEN** the user runs `agentcube invoke`\\n29: - **THEN** the system SHALL raise a `ValueError` indicating the agent has not been published\\n30: \\n31: ### Requirement: `status` command\\n32: \\n33: The system SHALL provide a `status` subcom...\n  Line 11: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775857492302,\"sessionID\":\"ses_286a547f1ffeZpobFdTX1gJ7fx\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d795adcc6001aSj2VQMsulFOhf\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d795ac4cf001rXStxP6u3Htbfl\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_286a547f1ffeZpobFdTX1gJ7fx\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"call_37f1ec61dc3449f392ab3f89\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-023/tasks.md\"},\"output\":\"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-023/tasks.md</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: # AR-023 — CLI invoke/status 命令 — Tasks\\n2: \\n3: > **Module:** cmd/cli\\n4: > **Language:** Python\\n5: > **Size:** M\\n6: > **Precondition:** Stage ST-3 (Design) completed\\n7: > **Reference:** `changes/AR-023/proposal.md`, `changes/AR-023/design.md`, `changes/AR-023/delta-spec.md`\\n8: > **Dependency:** AR-022 (publish command) — requires published agent endpoint\\n9: \\n10: ## T1. 实现 InvokeRuntime 类\\n11: \\n12: - [ ] 1.1 创建 `cmd/cli/agentcube/runtime/invoke_runtime.py`\\n13: - [ ] 1.2 定义 `InvokeRuntime` 类：`__init__(self, verbose: bool = False)`\\n14: - [ ] 1.3 实现 `invoke(self, workspace_path: Path, **options: Any) -> Dict[str, Any]`：\\n15:   - 加载 `agent_metadata.yaml`\\n16:   - 校验 `agent_endpoint` 存在 → 否则 `ValueError`\\n17:   - 发送 HTTP POST 请求到 endpoint\\n18:   - 返回响应结果\\n19: - [ ] 1.4 创建对应测试文件\\n20: \\n21: **Verification:** `pytest cmd/cli/tests/runtime/test_invoke_runtime.py -v` 全部通过\\n22: \\n23: ---\\n24: \\n25: ## T2. 增强 StatusRuntime 类\\n26: \\n27: - [ ] 2.1 修改 `cmd/cli/agentcube/runtime/status_runtime.py`\\n28: - [ ] 2.2 实现 `status(self, workspace_path: Path, **options: Any) -> Dict[str, Any]`：\\n29:   - 加载 `agent_metadata.yaml`\\n30:   - 根据 `k8s_deployment.type` 路由到正确的状态查询\\n31:   - 返回状态信息\\n32: - [ ] 2.3 实现/增强 `_get_cr_k8s_status(self, metadata) -> Dict[str, Any]`\\n33: - [ ] 2.4 创建对应测试文件\\n34: \\n35: **Verification:** `pytest cmd/cli/tests/runtime/test_status_runt...\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/results/runs/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z_logs/AR-023_ST-7.log:\n  Line 4: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775857429817,\"sessionID\":\"ses_286a623ebffexQ6eQhlYTCp58v\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7959ebec001MEozH9wxksxgOt\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7959dd24001YQnfO0w3R0jX9X\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_286a623ebffexQ6eQhlYTCp58v\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"glob\",\"callID\":\"call_f1cd87651f5f4d32a03097e1\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"pattern\":\"**/*AR-023*\"},\"output\":\"No files found\",\"metadata\":{\"count\":0,\"truncated\":false},\"title\":\"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z\",\"time\":{\"start\":1775857429798,\"end\":1775857429815}}}}\n  Line 7: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775857431249,\"sessionID\":\"ses_286a623ebffexQ6eQhlYTCp58v\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7959f17d0012bVZZ10THVxk4n\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7959dd24001YQnfO0w3R0jX9X\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_286a623ebffexQ6eQhlYTCp58v\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"grep\",\"callID\":\"call_4c09aada2e054f96abd30064\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"pattern\":\"AR-023\"},\"output\":\"Found 11 matches\\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/tasks.md:\\n  Line 1: # AR-023: CLI invoke/status 命令 — Tasks\\n\\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-023/design.md:\\n  Line 1: # AR-023 — CLI invoke/status 命令 — Design\\n  Line 174: **Known issue**: The existing implementation only assigns `response` inside `if endpoint.startswith(\\\"http\\\"):` — if the condition is false, `return response` raises `UnboundLocalError`. This is out of scope for AR-023 but the CLI layer will catch it via `_handle_error`.\\n  Line 669: 7. **Known UnboundLocalError**: `InvokeRuntime._invoke_agent_via_agentcube` has a known bug where `response` is only assigned inside `if endpoint.startswith(\\\"http\\\"):`. If the endpoint doesn't start with `http`, `return response` raises `UnboundLocalError`. This is out of scope for AR-023 — the CLI layer catches it via `_handle_error` and the user sees a friendly error message.\\n\\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/.sdd_prompt.md:\\n  Line 3: AR: AR-023 — CLI invoke/status 命令\\n\\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/delta-spec.md:\\n  Line 1: # AR-023: CLI invoke/status 命令 — Delta Spec\\n\\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/proposal.md:\\n  Line 1: # AR-023: CLI invoke/status 命令\\n\\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-023/tasks.md:\\n  Line 1: # AR-023 — CLI invoke/s...\n  Line 8: {\"type\":\"text\",\"timestamp\":1775857431343,\"sessionID\":\"ses_286a623ebffexQ6eQhlYTCp58v\",\"part\":{