nID\":\"ses_286c0c990ffeBZf2OlQ192KZ54\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"write\",\"callID\":\"call_a8454cadce1a4a70852a6abd\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"error\",\"input\":{\"content\":\"# Delta Spec: AR-023 — CLI invoke/status 命令\\n\\n## Context\\n\\n- **AR**: AR-023\\n- **Module**: cmd/cli\\n- **Language**: Python\\n- **Size**: M\\n- **Base spec**: cli-toolkit/spec.md, cli-toolkit/design.md\\n\\n## Scope\\n\\nThis delta spec covers the `invoke` and `status` CLI commands, their runtime classes (`InvokeRuntime`, `StatusRuntime`), and associated provider integrations (`AgentCubeProvider`, `KubernetesProvider`).\\n\\n---\\n\\n## invoke Command\\n\\n### Requirement: invoke command entry point\\n\\nThe system SHALL provide an `invoke` subcommand that POSTs JSON payload to the published agent endpoint, supporting both `agentcube` (AgentRuntime CR) and `k8s` (Deployment/Service) providers.\\n\\n#### Scenario: invoke options and defaults\\n\\n- **GIVEN** the user runs `invoke`\\n- **THEN** defaults SHALL be:\\n  - `workspace` = `\\\".\\\"` (`-f` / `--workspace`, `str`)\\n  - `payload` = `\\\"{}\\\"` (`--payload`, `str`)\\n  - `header_list` = `None` (`--header`, repeatable `List[str]`)\\n  - `provider` = `\\\"agentcube\\\"` (`--provider`, `str`)\\n  - `verbose` = `False` (`--verbose`, `bool`)\\n\\n#### Scenario: payload JSON parsing\\n\\n- **GIVEN** the user provides `--payload '{\\\"input\\\": \\\"hello\\\"}'`\\n- **WHEN** the command parses it\\n- **THEN** the system SHALL deserialize it to `{\\\"input\\\": \\\"hello\\\"}` and pass it to `InvokeRuntime.invoke`\\n\\n#### Scenario: invalid payload JSON\\n\\n- **GIVEN** `--payload` is not valid JSON (e.g., `--payload '{bad}'`)\\n- **WHEN** the command parses it\\n- **THEN** the CLI SHALL print `Error: Invalid JSON payload: {detail}` in red and exit with code `1` (before calling `_handle_error`)\\n\\n#### Scenario: header parsing\\n\\n- **GIVEN**...\n  Line 16: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775855800560,\"sessionID\":\"ses_286c0c990ffeBZf2OlQ192KZ54\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d79404fd4001TY4kSRGOQ6lt3l\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d794041bb001YRsZSUxJKuSvti\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_286c0c990ffeBZf2OlQ192KZ54\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"write\",\"callID\":\"call_0ee1d15369c249aa83338297\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"content\":\"# AR-023: CLI invoke/status 命令 — Delta Spec\\n\\n## Context\\n\\n- **Module:** `cmd/cli`\\n- **Language:** Python\\n- **Size:** M\\n- **Base specs:** `cli-toolkit/spec.md`, `cli-toolkit/design.md`\\n\\n## Scope\\n\\nThis delta spec covers the `invoke` and `status` CLI commands, their runtime classes (`InvokeRuntime`, `StatusRuntime`), and associated provider integrations (`AgentCubeProvider`, `KubernetesProvider`).\\n\\n---\\n\\n## invoke Command\\n\\n### Requirement: invoke command entry point\\n\\nThe system SHALL provide an `invoke` subcommand that POSTs JSON payload to the published agent endpoint, supporting both `agentcube` (AgentRuntime CR) and `k8s` (Deployment/Service) providers.\\n\\n#### Scenario: invoke options and defaults\\n\\n- **GIVEN** the user runs `invoke`\\n- **THEN** defaults SHALL be:\\n  - `workspace` = `\\\".\\\"` (`-f` / `--workspace`, `str`)\\n  - `payload` = `\\\"{}\\\"` (`--payload`, `str`)\\n  - `header_list` = `None` (`--header`, repeatable `List[str]`)\\n  - `provider` = `\\\"agentcube\\\"` (`--provider`, `str`)\\n  - `verbose` = `False` (`--verbose`, `bool`)\\n\\n#### Scenario: payload JSON parsing\\n\\n- **GIVEN** the user provides `--payload '{\\\"input\\\": \\\"hello\\\"}'`\\n- **WHEN** the command parses it\\n- **THEN** the system SHALL deserialize it to `{\\\"input\\\": \\\"hello\\\"}` and pass it to `InvokeRuntime.invoke`\\n\\n#### Scenario: invalid payload JSON\\n\\n- **GIVEN** `--payload` is not valid JSON (e.g., `--payload '{bad}'`)\\n- **WHEN** the command parses it\\n- **THEN** the CLI SHALL print `Error: Invalid JSON payload: {detail}` in red and exit with code `1` (before calling `_handle_error`)\\n\\n#### Scenario: header parsing\\n\\n- **GIVEN** the us...\n  Line 19: {\"type\":\"text\",\"timestamp\":1775855808923,\"sessionID\":\"ses_286c0c990ffeBZf2OlQ192KZ54\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7941236a001AB5qwUB2M6yPTc\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7941112d001jT0s09GoE3OW8j\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_286c0c990ffeBZf2OlQ192KZ54\",\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Done. `delta-spec.md` written with GIVEN/WHEN/THEN scenarios for AR-023 covering:\\n\\n- **invoke command**: options/defaults, payload JSON parsing, header parsing/validation, session header injection, AgentCube URL rewriting, prerequisites validation, success/error handling\\n- **status command**: options/defaults, not-published status, AgentRuntime CR status (3 variants), standard K8s status, Rich table display, error handling\\n- **InvokeRuntime class**: constructor, invoke method flow, `_validate_invoke_prerequisites`, `_invoke_agent_via_agentcube`, `_direct_http_invocation`\\n- **StatusRuntime class**: constructor, `get_status` flow, `_get_cr_k8s_status` (existing CR/no status/missing), `_get_k8s_status`\\n- **Cross-cutting**: `_handle_error` verbose traceback, provider selection (`agentcube` vs `k8s`)\",\"time\":{\"start\":1775855808922,\"end\":1775855808922}}}\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/results/runs/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z_logs/AR-023_ST-1.log:\n  Line 4: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775855542746,\"sessionID\":\"ses_286c2ea1effe1QQbhGSwQkN7CN\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d793d1d690010Jzvq10pyqdmAO\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d793d16cc001X7oDW1hTHFUFdm\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_286c2ea1effe1QQbhGSwQkN7CN\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"call_e84cb18a352d4b3494cdc651\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/.sdd_prompt.md\"},\"output\":\"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/.sdd_prompt.md</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: Write proposal.md for the agentcube project:\\n2: \\n3: AR: AR-023 — CLI invoke/status 命令\\n4: Module: cmd/cli\\n5: Language: Python\\n6: Size: M\\n7: \\n8: Relevant specs:\\n9: --- cli-toolkit/design.md ---\\n10: # AgentCube CLI (cli-toolkit) — Design\\n11: \\n12: Source root: `/tmp/agentcube-ref/cmd/cli/`.\\n13: \\n14: ## Package layout (every module path and role)\\n15: \\n16: | Path | Role |\\n17: |------|------|\\n18: | `pyproject.toml` | Project metadata, dependencies, console script mapping |\\n19: | `agentcube/__init__.py` | Package version `__version__`, exports `app`, runtimes |\\n20: | `agentcube/cli/__init__.py` | CLI subpackage marker |\\n21: | `agentcube/cli/main.py` | Typer `app`, all commands, `_handle_error`, `version_callback` |\\n22: | `agentcube/models/pack_models.py` | `MetadataOptions` dataclass |\\n23: | `agentcube/runtime/__init__.py` | Re-exports runtimes + `MetadataOptions` |\\n24: | `agentcube/runtime/pack_runtime.py` | `PackRuntime` |\\n25: | `agentcube/runtime/build_runtime.py` | `BuildRuntime` |\\n26: | `agentcube/runtime/publish_runtime.py` | `PublishRuntime` |\\n27: | `agentcube/runtime/invoke_runtime.py` | `InvokeRuntime` |\\n28: | `agentcube/runtime/status_runtime.py` | `StatusRuntime` |\\n29: | `agentcube/services/__init__.py` | Services package docstring |\\n30: | `agentcube/services/metadata_service.py` | `AgentMetadata`, `MetadataService` |\\n31: | `agent...\n  Line 7: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775855581390,\"sessionID\":\"ses_286c2ea1effe1QQbhGSwQkN7CN\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d793d4dc2001VJIthx77JFVdDr\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d793d223a001299b3mA5GrC45n\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_286c2ea1effe1QQbhGSwQkN7CN\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"write\",\"callID\":\"call_38398f55f29143f5884516b4\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"error\",\"input\":{\"content\":\"# Proposal: AR-023 — CLI invoke/status 命令\\n\\n## Summary\\n\\n实现 `kubectl-agentcube` CLI 的 `invoke` 和 `status` 两个子命令，支持通过 AgentCube Provider（AgentRuntime CR）和标准 Kubernetes Provider 调用已部署的 Agent 并查询其运行状态。\\n\\n## Problem\\n\\n当前 CLI 已实现 `pack`、`build`、`publish` 命令，完成了 Agent 从打包到部署的生命周期。缺少部署后的 **调用（invoke）** 和 **状态查询（status）** 能力，用户无法通过 CLI 验证 Agent 是否正常工作或查看其运行状态。\\n\\n## Goals\\n\\n1. **`invoke` 命令**：向已部署的 Agent 发送 HTTP POST 请求，支持 JSON payload、自定义 Header、AgentCube CR 路径重写\\n2. **`status` 命令**：加载 workspace 元数据，通过 Rich Table 展示 Agent 部署状态，支持 AgentCube CR 和标准 K8s 两种 Provider\\n3. 复用现有 `InvokeRuntime` 和 `StatusRuntime` 类，遵循已有 spec 定义的错误处理模式\\n\\n## Non-Goals\\n\\n- 不修改 `InvokeRuntime` / `StatusRuntime` 的内部实现逻辑（已知 `_invoke_agent_via_agentcube` 的 UnboundLocalError 问题不在本 AR 范围）\\n- 不新增 Provider 类型\\n- 不涉及 SDK 层改动\\n\\n## Design\\n\\n### invoke 命令\\n\\n```\\nkubectl-agentcube invoke [OPTIONS]\\n```\\n\\n**参数映射**（与 spec 一致）：\\n\\n| 参数 | 类型 | 默认值 | 说明 |\\n|------|------|--------|------|\\n| `-f, --workspace` | `str` | `\\\".\\\"` | Agent workspace 路径 |\\n| `--payload` | `str` | `\\\"{}\\\"` | JSON 格式输入 |\\n| `--header` | `List[str]` | `None` | 自定义 HTTP Header（可重复） |\\n| `--provider` | `str` | `\\\"agentcube\\\"` | `agentcube` 或 `k8s` |\\n| `--verbose` | `bool` | `False` | 详细日志 |\\n\\n**CLI 层职责**（`agentcube/cli/main.py`）：\\n\\n1. 解析 `--payload` 为 JSON，失败时打印错误并 `typer.Exit(1)`\\n2. 解析 `--header` 列表为 `Dict[str, str]`，格式校验失败时打印错误并 `typer.Exit(1)`\\n3. 实例化 `InvokeRuntime(verbose=verbose, provider=provider)`\\n4. 调用 `runtime.invoke(workspace_path, payload, headers)`\\n5. 打印响应结果（JSON 序列化），异常走 `_handle_error`\\n\\n**InvokeRuntime 层职责**（已有实现，CLI 仅调用）：\\n\\n- `_validate_invoke_prerequisites`：验证 workspace 存在、元数...\n  Line 10: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775855612463,\"sessionID\":\"ses_286c2ea1effe1QQbhGSwQkN7CN\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d793dc8ad001UjVjICIa7qxJme\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d793db91d001R9IttFkyA6Fj6G\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_286c2ea1effe1QQbhGSwQkN7CN\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"write\",\"callID\":\"call_7251a7dc635840869ecf78c0\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"error\",\"input\":{\"content\":\"# Proposal: AR-023 — CLI invoke/status 命令\\n\\n## Summary\\n\\n实现 `kubectl-agentcube` CLI 的 `invoke` 和 `status` 两个子命令，支持通过 AgentCube Provider（AgentRuntime CR）和标准 Kubernetes Provider 调用已部署的 Agent 并查询其运行状态。\\n\\n## Problem\\n\\n当前 CLI 已实现 `pack`、`build`、`publish` 命令，完成了 Agent 从打包到部署的生命周期。缺少部署后的 **调用（invoke）** 和 **状态查询（status）** 能力，用户无法通过 CLI 验证 Agent 是否正常工作或查看其运行状态。\\n\\n## Goals\\n\\n1. **`invoke` 命令**：向已部署的 Agent 发送 HTTP POST 请求，支持 JSON payload、自定义 Header、AgentCube CR 路径重写\\n2. **`status` 命令**：加载 workspace 元数据，通过 Rich Table 展示 Agent 部署状态，支持 AgentCube CR 和标准 K8s 两种 Provider\\n3. 复用现有 `InvokeRuntime` 和 `StatusRuntime` 类，遵循已有 spec 定义的错误处理模式\\n\\n## Non-Goals\\n\\n- 不修改 `InvokeRuntime` / `StatusRuntime` 的内部实现逻辑（已知 `_invoke_agent_via_agentcube` 的 UnboundLocalError 问题不在本 AR 范围）\\n- 不新增 Provider 类型\\n- 不涉及 SDK 层改动\\n\\n## Design\\n\\n### invoke 命令\\n\\n```\\nkubectl-agentcube invoke [OPTIONS]\\n```\\n\\n**参数映射**（与 spec 一致）：\\n\\n| 参数 | 类型 | 默认值 | 说明 |\\n|------|------|--------|------|\\n| `-f, --workspace` | `str` | `\\\".\\\"` | Agent workspace 路径 |\\n| `--payload` | `str` | `\\\"{}\\\"` | JSON 格式输入 |\\n| `--header` | `List[str]` | `None` | 自定义 HTTP Header（可重复） |\\n| `--provider` | `str` | `\\\"agentcube\\\"` | `agentcube` 或 `k8s` |\\n| `--verbose` | `bool` | `False` | 详细日志 |\\n\\n**CLI 层职责**（`agentcube/cli/main.py`）：\\n\\n1. 解析 `--payload` 为 JSON，失败时打印错误并 `typer.Exit(1)`\\n2. 解析 `--header` 列表为 `Dict[str, str]`，格式校验失败时打印错误并 `typer.Exit(1)`\\n3. 实例化 `InvokeRuntime(verbose=verbose, provider=provider)`\\n4. 调用 `runtime.invoke(workspace_path, payload, headers)`\\n5. 打印响应结果（JSON 序列化），异常走 `_handle_error`\\n\\n**InvokeRuntime 层职责**（已有实现，CLI 仅调用）：\\n\\n- `_validate_invoke_prerequisites`：验证 workspace 存在、元数...\n  Line 19: {\"type\":\"text\",\"timestamp\":1775855671539,\"sessionID\":\"ses_286c2ea1effe1QQbhGSwQkN7CN\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d793e56ef00120X1MoQneDrsrv\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d793e4b9d001OnVnd6uhODZ3t0\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_286c2ea1effe1QQbhGSwQkN7CN\",\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Now I understand the context. The existing `proposal.md` is for AR-019. I need to update it for AR-023.\",\"time\":{\"start\":1775855671537,\"end\":1775855671537}}}\n  Line 20: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775855671584,\"sessionID\":\"ses_286c2ea1effe1QQbhGSwQkN7CN\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d793e591d001RVohvQ4E0Cykhh\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d793e4b9d001OnVnd6uhODZ3t0\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_286c2ea1effe1QQbhGSwQkN7CN\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"write\",\"callID\":\"call_25cd9a70e2494c28ab230078\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"content\":\"# AR-023: CLI invoke/status 命令\\n\\n## Purpose\\n\\n为 AgentCube Python CLI（`kubectl-agentcube`）实现 `invoke` 和 `status` 两个子命令，补全 Agent 从打包、构建、发布到调用和状态查询的完整生命周期。\\n\\n当前 CLI 已实现 `pack`、`build`、`publish` 命令，但用户部署 Agent 后无法通过 CLI 验证其是否正常工作或查看运行状态。本 AR 补齐最后两个关键操作。\\n\\n## Scope\\n\\n### In Scope\\n\\n1. **`invoke` 命令**\\n   - 向已部署的 Agent 发送 HTTP POST 请求\\n   - 支持 `--payload` 传递 JSON 输入（默认 `\\\"{}\\\"`）\\n   - 支持 `--header` 添加自定义 HTTP Header（可重复指定）\\n   - 支持 `--provider` 选择 `agentcube`（AgentRuntime CR）或 `k8s`（标准 Deployment/Service）\\n   - AgentCube Provider 自动将 endpoint 重写为 `/v1/namespaces/{namespace}/agent-runtimes/{agent_name}/invocations/`\\n   - 若元数据包含 `session_id`，自动添加 `X-Agentcube-Session-Id` Header\\n   - 打印响应结果，异常通过 `_handle_error` 处理\\n\\n2. **`status` 命令**\\n   - 加载 workspace 元数据（`agent_metadata.yaml`）\\n   - 根据 `--provider` 查询对应资源状态\\n   - AgentCube Provider：通过 `AgentCubeProvider.get_agent_runtime` 查询 CR 状态\\n   - K8s Provider：通过 `KubernetesProvider.get_agent_status` 查询 Deployment/Service 状态\\n   - 使用 Rich Table 渲染状态信息\\n   - `not_published` 或 `error` 状态时打印提示并 `typer.Exit(1)`\\n\\n3. **错误处理**\\n   - `invoke`：JSON payload 解析失败、Header 格式错误直接退出码 1\\n   - 运行时异常统一走 `_handle_error(e, command_name, verbose)`\\n\\n### Out of Scope\\n\\n- 修复 `InvokeRuntime._invoke_agent_via_agentcube` 的已知 UnboundLocalError（条件分支未覆盖非 http 开头的 endpoint）\\n- 新增 Provider 类型\\n- SDK 层改动\\n- Python CLI 以外的组件（Go CLI、Controller 等）\\n\\n## Impact Analysis\\n\\n### Dependencies\\n\\n| 依赖 | 用途 | 影响 |\\n|------|------|------|\\n| `InvokeRuntime`（已有） | invoke 核心逻辑 | 无影响，CLI 仅调用 |\\n| `StatusRuntime`（已有） | status 核心逻辑 | 无影响，CLI 仅调用 |\\n| `AgentCubeProvider`（已有） | CR 查询 | 无影响 |\\n| `KubernetesProvider`（已有） | 标准 K8s ...\n  Line 23: {\"type\":\"text\",\"timestamp\":1775855676979,\"sessionID\":\"ses_286c2ea1effe1QQbhGSwQkN7CN\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d793f26c8001y2G4XjTmV8Bj42\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d793f194d001873QZDUm2qEE9j\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_286c2ea1effe1QQbhGSwQkN7CN\",\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"`proposal.md` 已写入。内容涵盖 AR-023 的 `invoke` 和 `status` 命令实现方案，包括：\\n\\n- **Summary**：补全 Agent 生命周期最后的调用和状态查询能力\\n- **Design**：CLI 层参数解析 → 调用现有 `InvokeRuntime`/`StatusRuntime` → 结果展示\\n- **实现代码**：两个命令的完整 Python 实现草稿\\n- **错误处理**：JSON/Header 解析错误直接退出，运行时异常走 `_handle_error`\\n- **验收标准**：invoke 和 status 各 9 项检查点\",\"time\":{\"start\":1775855676977,\"end\":1775855676977}}}\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/results/runs/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z_logs/AR-023_ST-0.log:\n  Line 14: {\"type\":\"text\",\"timestamp\":1775855471966,\"sessionID\":\"ses_286c4542affeXH9FMzi8iYj0mq\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d793c095b001N2N3Zk1O23C7UC\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d793be14c001LNw510daIOUYXZ\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_286c4542affeXH9FMzi8iYj0mq\",\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Now I'll create the scaffold directory with the 4 standard files for AR-023.\",\"time\":{\"start\":1775855471965,\"end\":1775855471965}}}\n  Line 15: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775855471984,\"sessionID\":\"ses_286c4542affeXH9FMzi8iYj0mq\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d793c0a32001Kd3CjSkpYHkOAj\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d793be14c001LNw510daIOUYXZ\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_286c4542affeXH9FMzi8iYj0mq\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"bash\",\"callID\":\"call_6adf9837728d48c7bbbc87f2\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"command\":\"mkdir -p /home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-023\",\"description\":\"Create AR-023 change directory\"},\"output\":\"\",\"metadata\":{\"output\":\"\",\"exit\":0,\"description\":\"Create AR-023 change directory\",\"truncated\":false},\"title\":\"Create AR-023 change directory\",\"time\":{\"start\":1775855471897,\"end\":1775855471981}}}}\n  Line 18: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775855483258,\"sessionID\":\"ses_286c4542affeXH9FMzi8iYj0mq\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d793c1d10001H1Rx5RK67qMgyS\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d793c0da8001uQPeOwVCEfsHtY\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_286c4542affeXH9FMzi8iYj0mq\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"write\",\"callID\":\"call_b76f17ee3c084ee4a5e1ac62\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"content\":\"# AR-023 — CLI invoke/status 命令\\n\\n**Module:** cmd/cli\\n**Language:** Python\\n**Size:** M\\n\\n## 目的\\n\\n为 AgentCube CLI (`kubectl-agentcube`) 实现 `invoke` 和 `status` 两个子命令。`invoke` 用于向已部署的 agent 发送请求并获取响应，`status` 用于查询 agent 的运行状态和部署信息。\\n\\n## 范围\\n\\n### 包含\\n\\n1. `invoke` Typer 命令实现\\n2. `status` Typer 命令实现\\n3. `InvokeRuntime` 类实现\\n4. `StatusRuntime` 类增强\\n\\n### 不包含\\n\\n- `pack` / `build` / `publish` 命令的实现（由 AR-020 / AR-021 / AR-022 覆盖）\\n- Go 二进制入口\\n- CI/CD pipeline 变更\\n\\n## 架构概要\\n\\n```\\nCLI Layer (Typer)\\n├── invoke() command → InvokeRuntime.invoke()\\n└── status() command → StatusRuntime.status()\\n\\nRuntime Layer\\n├── InvokeRuntime — 发送 HTTP 请求到已部署的 agent endpoint\\n└── StatusRuntime — 查询 K8s CR 或 Deployment 状态\\n```\\n\\n## 上游依赖\\n\\n- **AR-022 (`publish` 命令)** — 依赖 publish 部署后的 agent endpoint 和 metadata\\n\\n## 状态\\n\\n- [ ] 提案审查\\n- [ ] 实现\\n- [ ] 验证\\n\",\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-023/proposal.md\"},\"output\":\"Wrote file successfully.\",\"metadata\":{\"diagnostics\":{},\"filepath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-023/proposal.md\",\"exists\":false,\"truncated\":false},\"title\":\"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-023/proposal.md\",\"time\":{\"start\":1775855483244,\"end\":1775855483256}}}}\n  Line 19: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775855492972,\"sessionID\":\"ses_286c4542affeXH9FMzi8iYj0mq\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d793c39f4001QJNDHQOwkR20vm\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d793c0da8001uQPeOwVCEfsHtY\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_286c4542affeXH9FMzi8iYj0mq\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"write\",\"callID\":\"call_8367e9ceecfc4394998aa421\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"content\":\"# AR-023 — CLI invoke/status 命令 — Design\\n\\n## Overview\\n\\nThe `invoke` command sends requests to a deployed agent endpoint and displays the response.\\nThe `status` command queries the deployment status of an agent from Kubernetes or metadata.\\n\\n## Architecture\\n\\n### Data Flow\\n\\n```\\ninvoke() CLI → InvokeRuntime.invoke() → HTTP request to agent_endpoint → Rich output\\nstatus() CLI → StatusRuntime.status() → K8s API / metadata → Rich status table\\n```\\n\\n### Package Layout\\n\\n```\\ncmd/cli/\\n├── agentcube/\\n│   ├── cli/\\n│   │   └── main.py                    — invoke() and status() commands\\n│   ├── runtime/\\n│   │   ├── invoke_runtime.py          — InvokeRuntime class\\n│   │   └── status_runtime.py          — StatusRuntime class (enhanced)\\n│   └── services/\\n│       ├── agentcube_provider.py      — get_agent_runtime() for status\\n│       └── k8s_provider.py            — get_agent_status() for status\\n```\\n\\n## Component Design\\n\\n### InvokeRuntime\\n\\n```python\\nclass InvokeRuntime:\\n    def __init__(self, verbose: bool = False) -> None: ...\\n    def invoke(self, workspace_path: Path, **options: Any) -> Dict[str, Any]: ...\\n```\\n\\n### StatusRuntime\\n\\n```python\\nclass StatusRuntime:\\n    def __init__(self, verbose: bool = False) -> None: ...\\n    def status(self, workspace_path: Path, **options: Any) -> Dict[str, Any]: ...\\n    def _get_cr_k8s_status(self, metadata) -> Dict[str, Any]: ...\\n```\\n\\n## Testing Strategy\\n\\n- Unit tests for InvokeRuntime and StatusRuntime\\n- CLI command tests for invoke and status\\n- Mock HTTP responses for invoke\\n- Mock K8s API for status\\n\\n## Implementation Notes\\n\\n1. `invoke` loads endpoin...\n  Line 20: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775855505855,\"sessionID\":\"ses_286c4542affeXH9FMzi8iYj0mq\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d793c6034001ESKyU72OkqzwgA\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d793c0da8001uQPeOwVCEfsHtY\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_286c4542affeXH9FMzi8iYj0mq\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"write\",\"callID\":\"call_b56cfa4372b740ad8680fa02\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"content\":\"# AR-023: CLI invoke/status 命令 — Delta Spec\\n\\n## Context\\n\\n- **Module:** `cmd/cli`\\n- **Language:** Python\\n- **Size:** M\\n- **Base specs:** `cli-toolkit/design.md`, `cli-toolkit/spec.md`\\n\\n## Delta Requirements\\n\\n### Requirement: `invoke` command\\n\\nThe system SHALL provide an `invoke` subcommand that sends an HTTP request to a deployed agent endpoint.\\n\\n#### Scenario: Command signature\\n- **GIVEN** the CLI is installed\\n- **WHEN** the user runs `agentcube invoke --help`\\n- **THEN** it SHALL show options for workspace, input/prompt, and verbose\\n\\n#### Scenario: Invoke with endpoint from metadata\\n- **GIVEN** the workspace has been published and `agent_metadata.yaml` contains `agent_endpoint`\\n- **WHEN** the user runs `agentcube invoke -f <workspace> --prompt \\\"hello\\\"`\\n- **THEN** the system SHALL send an HTTP POST request to the endpoint and display the response\\n\\n#### Scenario: Invoke without published endpoint\\n- **GIVEN** the workspace has not been published or `agent_endpoint` is missing\\n- **WHEN** the user runs `agentcube invoke`\\n- **THEN** the system SHALL raise a `ValueError` indicating the agent has not been published\\n\\n### Requirement: `status` command\\n\\nThe system SHALL provide a `status` subcommand that queries the deployment status of an agent.\\n\\n#### Scenario: Command signature\\